<h2 class="bold font-l">Naofumi's Trial</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Naofumi is accused of rape by Myne, his attractive red-haired adventuring partner, and his pleas to the contrary are ignored. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/FalseRapeAccusation" class='trope-example-link'>False Rape Accusation</a></p>
</div>
