</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="dno5k0" data-video-descrip="The kingdom Naofumi finds himself trapped in practices human supremacy and BeastMan and Demihuman are offered as slaves to perform menial labor or serve as body guards. They are sealed with a curse that forces obedience. At the end of the episode, Naofumi comes across a shady merchant offering slaves for sale. While Naofumi initially rejects the offer, when the Slave Trader points out that slaves cannot lie or betray their masters, Naofumi chooses to listen and looks over the slaves." data-video-title="The Slave Merchant" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/dno5k0_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/dno5k0.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/HumanTraffickers" data-video-tropename="Human Traffickers" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Recap/TheRisingOfTheShieldHeroS1E1TheShieldHero,LightNovel/TheRisingOfTheShieldHero" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/dno5k0.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">The Slave Merchant</span></p>
</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="yf7ntq" data-video-descrip="Feeling that death is too light a punishment for the crimes they committed, Naofumi proposes an alternative solution: That Aultcray change his name to Trash and Malty to Bitch, with Slut/Whore as her adventuring name, thus making their true natures public for all to see." data-video-title="Aultcray and Myne get renamed" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/yf7ntq_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/yf7ntq.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/MeaningfulRename" data-video-tropename="Meaningful Rename" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="LightNovel/TheRisingOfTheShieldHero" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/yf7ntq.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">Aultcray and My...</span></p>
</a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="alt-titles section section-fact">
<h3>
<strong>Alternative Title(s):</strong>
<span>Tate No Yuusha No Nariagari</span>, <span>The Rising Of The Shield Hero</span> </h3>
